 you actually see</i>

00:02:10.729 --> 00:02:13.499
<i> the north wall of Gale Crater.</i>

00:02:13.499 --> 00:02:15.801
<i> So, we are trying to look
 at these rocks</i>

00:02:15.801 --> 00:02:18.170
<i> with the rover and trying to
 understand the history</i>

00:02:18.170 --> 00:02:20.039
<i> that they are telling us
 about this place.</i>

00:02:20.039 --> 00:02:22.908
<i> Here's another place
 we call this one Shaler</i>

00:02:22.908 --> 00:02:24.610
<i> and this is layered rocks,</i>

