This is a story of...

00:03:15.528 --> 00:03:17.296
we are right there
by the bed rock,

00:03:17.296 --> 00:03:20.032
it is right under our feet,
we can drive up to it,

00:03:20.032 --> 00:03:21.567
we can read this history,

00:03:21.567 --> 00:03:25.304
but we do have to deal with
this veneer of dust and sand,

00:03:25.304 --> 00:03:28.007
and pebbles here and there.

00:03:28.007 --> 00:03:30.243
Wind erosion
is a big deal in Gale

00:03:30.243 --> 00:03:32.611
