That rock broke apart,
made sand and pebbles

00:04:13.018 --> 00:04:15.121
and cobbles and dust.

00:04:15.121 --> 00:04:19.058
And then, that stuff was
transported by wind or water

00:04:19.058 --> 00:04:21.160
